dev.marksman.kraftwerk.aggregator

Interface Aggregator<A,Builder,Out>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the element type
    Builder - the type of a temporary "builder" object. A builder may contain its own state.
    Out - the type of the final result

    public interface Aggregator<A,Builder,Out>
    Defines a strategy for constructing values that are an aggregate of an element type (e.g. collections).
